  "title": "Office Administrator",
  "description": "<p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Manage day-to-day office operations, including reception, meeting rooms, mail, and general office supplies.</li><li>Oversee facilities matters such as maintenance, cleaning, security access, and vendor coordination.</li><li>Support staff with administrative needs, including onboarding logistics and workspace setup.</li><li>Ensure compliance with firm policies, safety standards, and confidentiality requirements.</li><li>Liaise with building management and external service providers on office-related issues.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma or equivalent qualification in Business Administration or related field.</li><li>3+ years of experience in office administration, preferably in a professional services or legal environment.</li><li>Strong organizational and time-management skills with attention to detail.</li><li>Good communication skills and ability to interact professionally with internal and external stakeholders.</li><li>Proficiency in basic office software (e.g. Microsoft Office).</li></ul><p>If you have what it takes, please send your resume to syafiqah@ambition.com.sg or click APPLY NOW. Data provided is for recruitment purposes only. Regrettably, only shortlisted candidates will be notified.<br />Business Reg No : 200611680D | Licence No : 10C5117 | EA Reg No : R2199023</p>",
